(15, '799491-3255987', 'Application Fees', 'The application period for The Great Burlesque Exposition is open from August 22, 2014 through October 22, 2014.  Notifications to performers will go out on or about December 1, 2014.\n\n<B>Applications between August 22 and September 22 are $15 and we pay the ticketing fees; after September 22, they are $20 <I>plus</i> the ticketing fees!</B>\n\nThe Great Exposition will be held February 20-22, 2015 at The Hyatt Regency Hotel in Cambridge, MA.  Special guests include: Angie Pontani, Miss Exotic World 2008; eye-popping pop icon, Kitten Natividad; the out-of-this-world Ray Gunn; Nina La Voix; Whisper de Corvo; Red Velvet; Scarlet Starlet; Blaze, the Red Rose of Texas; Scandal from Bohemia; The Boston Babydolls; and more.', 0, '20.00', '2014-08-23 18:53:49', 'BPT Auto Import'),
